#: ../../source/developer_guide/Design_Documents/cpu_binding.md:197
msgid ""
"This layout remains deterministic even when different worker processes "
"share the same cpuset, because slicing is based on the global logical NPU"
" ID."
msgstr "即使不同工作进程共享相同的cpuset，此布局也保持确定性，因为切分是基于全局逻辑NPU ID的。"

